<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc337c53a-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s2063"><num value="2063">§ 2063.</num><heading> Employment assistance</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary may authorize homeless veterans receiving care through vocational rehabilitation programs to participate in the compensated work therapy program under <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s1718">section 1718 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc337c53b-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/107/95/s5/a/1">Pub. L. 107–95, § 5(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="2001-12-21">Dec. 21, 2001</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/115/914">115 Stat. 914</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
